saint john of las vegas is a 2009 american comedy-drama film starring steve buscemi , romany malco , and sarah silverman .   st. john of las vegas was the first film released by indievest pictures , a subsidiary of indievest .   the film , directed and written for the screen by hue rhodes ( based on a story by dante alighieri ) and produced by steve buscemi , stanley tucci , and spike lee , follows an ex-gambler as he takes a road trip with his new partner , an auto insurance fraud debunker , to investigate a fraud , while meeting a series of offbeat characters , including a carnival 's human torch , a paraplegic stripper , and a nude militant , along the way .   the film was shown in film festivals and was released in limited release on january 29 , 2010 .